From: Shawn Guo <shawn.guo@freescale.com>
Date: Thu, 25 Jul 2013 14:56:34 +0800
Subject: [PATCH 0213/1072] ENGR00269945: ARM: imx: enable SATA support in
 defconfig

git://git.freescale.com/imx/linux-2.6-imx.git imx_3.10.17_1.0.0_beta
commit e465ff09fa97824c03378155a4a97fafa37bcf17

Enable SATA support in imx_v6_v7_defconfig.

Signed-off-by: Shawn Guo <shawn.guo@freescale.com>
Signed-off-by: Hongbo Zhong <hongbo.zhong@windriver.com>
---
 arch/arm/configs/imx_v6_v7_defconfig |    2 ++
 1 files changed, 2 insertions(+), 0 deletions(-)

diff --git a/arch/arm/configs/imx_v6_v7_defconfig b/arch/arm/configs/imx_v6_v7_defconfig
index 81a3071..7ad37c9 100644
--- a/arch/arm/configs/imx_v6_v7_defconfig
+++ b/arch/arm/configs/imx_v6_v7_defconfig
@@ -100,6 +100,8 @@ CONFIG_SCSI_LOGGING=y
 CONFIG_SCSI_SCAN_ASYNC=y
 # CONFIG_SCSI_LOWLEVEL is not set
 CONFIG_ATA=y
+CONFIG_SATA_AHCI_PLATFORM=y
+CONFIG_AHCI_IMX=y
 CONFIG_PATA_IMX=y
 CONFIG_NETDEVICES=y
 # CONFIG_NET_VENDOR_BROADCOM is not set
